OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThe day will start with some
OL,6,Flow cloud, mist and fog patches
OL,7,Faround, though these should lift
OL,8,Freadily during the morning to leave a
OL,9,Ffine day across the region with sunny
OL,10,Fspells. Feeling quite hot in the
OL,11,Fgentle winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FThe fine weather will
OL,14,Fcontinue heading into the evening and
OL,15,Fovernight. It will remain dry with
OL,16,Fclear spells, although some patches of
OL,17,Flow cloud and fog are possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
